Over the last 10 years Jeanette Bronee and the Path for Life Program has made a strong positive difference in my total self (physical, emotional and spiritual).  Jeanette’s approach is always client-centered.  She’s devoted to delivering the best services and constantly expands her knowledge which means clients receive the best and most current products and information.  Her latest innovation is the on-line delivery of Path for Life’s program.  It’s filled with information along with tools and resources and Jeanette is only an E-mail or phone call away along with the opportunity to drop in for a face to face.

Alice Lilly
Devoted Client

originalText.text: Path For Life is true to its name, a way of life. Path For Life brilliantly composed by Jeanette Bronee has organized a belief system in regards to how to treat ones health just as we aim to be balanced with all that is living. Her multiple layered approach to teaching and learning about nutrition is linked to ones own personal patterns, how foods interact within the body, a gradual and definitive yet individual way of eating, what food actually is from grain to vegetable and an education about a whole current unhealthy system that we need to live in on the day to day. Path for Life taught me how to love food, its beauty, how it grows, how to combine its varieties, which are available and to never ever be hungry. Jeanette has written a holistic glossary, library one which can be accessed at all times for recipes, seasonal eating, deliberate choices according to ones time of life be it cycles of change or emotional urges. I have openly welcomed Path For Life into my life after being a product of numerous diets now celebrating nourishment as another aesthetic of our important and healthy participation in nature. Thank you Jeanette Bronee!

originalText.text: I visited Jeanette for general concerns with stress, low energy, and lack of motivation.  Her expertise and professionalism are only exceeded by her compassion and sense of humor.  She was attentive and kind, as well as challenging and stimulating.  I returned to her with some medical results and have implemented a new nutritional regime to address high cholesterol and some skin conditions.  I have seen a change in a short amount of time in both the mental and physical areas of my life.  I appreciate her accessibility, her skill, and her dedication.  And, I love her office.  Jeanette is a treasure and I am grateful our paths crossed!

originalText.text:
Jeanette Bronée guided me through recovery from cranial surgery in 2012. Even though I thought I had vague idea of good nutrition, when I became ill, and after the surgery, I didn't  have the energy to take care of myself. It was so great to rely on her expert advise tailor made for me as to what to eat, which supplements would aid my recovery.
I know many self taught wellness coaches, but I trust none other than Jeanette Bronée.
